title: Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth
itunes:title: Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth
description:
Boom! Don’t let the dog days of summer get you down, here’s another rad chat for you fine folks. Chadwick Johnson from Hundredth is on the show this week to discuss many things including evolving as a human being, playing a different style of music and the early years of playing in bands. It’s a very open and honest discussion that I was glad to have with him while he was on his tour bus. LISTEN AND LEARN! Simple Mobile is your perfect sidekick for all your summer adventures!Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!
